DOC.brief_summary: This study evaluate safety efficacy botulinum toxin Type A compare placebo treatment Crow 's Feet Lines Frown Lines ( Facial Rhytides )
DOC.brief_title: Safety Efficacy Study Botulinum Toxin Type A Treatment Crow 's Feet Lines Frown Lines
DOC.criteria: Moderate severe Crow 's Feet Lines Frown Lines Have adequate vision without use eyeglass assess facial wrinkle mirror ( contact lenses OK ) Current previous botulinum toxin treatment serotype Diagnosis myasthenia gravis , EatonLambert syndrome , amyotrophic lateral sclerosis Prior facial cosmetic surgery ( e.g. , prior periorbital surgery , facial lift , brow lift , eyelid lift eyebrow surgery ) Facial laser light treatment , microdermabrasion , superficial peel within 3 month Oral retinoid therapy within one year
